[Heart Failure - A Model for Multimorbidity].

[Article in German]

Güder G, Ertl G.

Heart failure frequently is the consequence of different cardiac diseases and is 
associated with multiple cardiac and non-cardiac co-morbidities. It may be 
exemplary for multi-morbidity in the elderly, has negative impact on various 
organ systems and may induce further comorbidities. The following article 
addresses heart failure as a multisystem disorder.

