Efficacy, safety, and clinical outcome of modern mechanical thrombectomy in 
elderly patients with acute ischemic stroke.

Son S(1), Kang DH(2)(3)(4), Hwang YH(4)(5), Kim YS(3)(4), Kim YW(6)(7)(8).

